{"tid":2064031,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【國際線總攻第二擊】國際和你THX正式徵兵","createTime":"2020-06-14T13:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T17:16:04.000Z","uid":33808,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"7ae4b5f7b283e99088dc069b11275b346a2d8e57","tid":2064031,"uid":33808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T13:25:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Hi！被捕手足再次需要大家幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢哋想搞一個<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">「國際和你THX」</span></span>大外宣！<br />\n需要大家一齊<span style=\"color: violet;\">建立香港嘅優良國際形象</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n繼承上年香港人全球登報嘅創舉<br />\n希望大家喺今個月寫大量明信片俾國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HwmTzmL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHwmTzmL.jpg&h=ac364083&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A1bo4pq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA1bo4pq.jpg&h=a5e37605&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EjuxXKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEjuxXKE.jpg&h=cb794381&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">之所以要向國際致謝係因為！</span></strong></div></span><br />\n<br />\n一，<span style=\"color: orange;\">如果確立到個主流嘅香港民族形象</span>，<span style=\"color: violet;\">無論五毛幾努力，極左幾偏激，都只會係少數例外</span>（勇武手足深明此道⋯⋯）<br />\n<br />\n二，<span style=\"color: orange;\">國際而家籌組緊反共勢力</span>，係對香港關注度最高嘅時候，<span style=\"color: violet;\">亦係奠定香港民族謙虛莊敬形象嘅關鍵時刻！</span><br />\n<br />\n三，<span style=\"color: orange;\">只有喺國際長期持續彰顯&mdash;&mdash;香港同中國有巨大而明顯嘅差異</span>，<span style=\"color: violet;\">世界先會覺得香港值得擁有屬於自己民族嘅自由！</span><br />\n<br />\n四，<span style=\"color: orange;\">支援被清算被捕嘅手足有本錢去繼續抗爭</span>，佢哋真係需要大家嘅<span style=\"color: violet;\">支持，先可以有能力抵抗政權全方位封殺</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔知大家仲記唔記得，<br />\n國際線而家係有大量五毛扮香港人屌鳩外國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">先有五毛出現</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Solomon Yue回應香港手足的不滿<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2033280\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2033280</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">後有on9附和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1590491155.A.E32.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1590491155.A.E32.html&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8mlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=57ee598b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1590491155.A.E32.html</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">我哋鄭重向全香港求援，<br />\n懇求大家加入呢場五毛+極左突破作戰！</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">我哋將會喺唔同黃店設置明信片收發站！</div></span></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">裡面<span style=\"color: pink;\">有指引</span>、<span style=\"color: teal;\">有郵票</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">有明信片</span>！<br />\n全部由文宣手足設計，手足包裝！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">一包18蚊，兩包35蚊，三包45蚊！<br />\n全數捐俾協助今次外宣嘅文宣手足<br />\n同埋支援流亡同被捕者</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HuGz3hz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHuGz3hz.jpg&h=811c515f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>合作黃店列表如下<br />\n（真係會持續更新，已多幾間應承咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</strong></span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://drive.google.com/file/d/19Xykf5Ls70AWSsq1DjcVXpnFOfkfQ0_6/view?usp=sharing&amp;hl=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F19Xykf5Ls70AWSsq1DjcVXpnFOfkfQ0_6%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing%26hl%3Den&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8mlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=a07e13c2\" target=\"_blank\">http://drive.google.com/file/d/19Xykf5Ls70AWSsq1DjcVXpnFOfkfQ0_6/view?usp=sharing&amp;hl=en</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">詳細教學</div></span></span></strong><br />\n第一步！<br />\nScan QRcode 拎建議地址<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LBx0epr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLBx0epr.jpg&h=c017d0fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二步！<br />\n<br />\n跟excel嘅翻譯寫當地語言嘅多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vis7DRd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVis7DRd.png&h=b35d81ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三步！<br />\n<br />\n貼我哋事先準備好嘅郵票！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OB6kesk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOB6kesk.jpg&h=64c2dd6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第四步！<br />\n<br />\n可以自寄或擺落收集箱～<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rrkEuYd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrrkEuYd.jpg&h=e0f860e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第五步！<br />\n可以上channel投返你揀嘅地址～<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/interthx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finterthx&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8mlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=bfddbc24\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/interthx</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">希望大家可以支援我哋，一齊繼全球登報之後，再次連結全世界！<br />\n進攻國際線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></div><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">多謝你睇到呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝你支持我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果想訂一批自己寫，<br />\n可以去我哋IG dm訂貨～</span></div></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">～不浪漫的香港告白～</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/alt.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Falt.hk%2F&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8mlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=4efee50c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/alt.hk/</a></div>"},{"pid":"96566eadaba443e8f256933f904c015291dd6af2","tid":2064031,"uid":178992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T13:26:53.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"95d743be30f762e8297c7e737d083060246ff597","tid":2064031,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T13:27:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a